{"lemma":"جِذْعَيْ","slug":"جِذْعَيْ","root":"ج.ذ.ع","root_slug":"ج-ذ-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ذ-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جِذْع","root":"جذع","pos":"N","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n5329","n5330"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%90%D8%B0%D9%92%D8%B9%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to stem"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a tree trunk, body, stock, torso","examples":[{"text":"وَهُزِّي إِلَيْكِ بِجِذْعِ النَّخْلَةِ تُسَاقِطْ عَلَيْكِ رُطَبًا جَنِيًّا","english":"Shake towards thee the palm’s trunk: it will drop ripe and fresh dates upon thee."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"youth, animal old enough to use (of livestock as well as humans)"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Cognate with Classical Syriac ܓܘܙܥܐ (guzʿā, “trunk”), Hebrew גֶּזַע (gézaʿ, “trunk, stock, race”)."},"ipa":["/d͡ʒað.ðaʕ/","/d͡ʒa.ðaʕ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n5329","headword_ar":"جِذْعٌ","root":"j*E","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trunk"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a palm-tree: (S, * Msb, K:) or, accord to some, only"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after it has become dry:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, accord. to some, only"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after it has been cut:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trunk"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a tree"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when the head has gone:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 656:) in the Kur, xix. 23, it is applied to the trunk of a palm-tree which had become dry and was without a head; (Bd;) therefore this does not indicate any restriction nor the contrary: (TA:) pl. [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^jo*aAEN","text_ar":"اجْذَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb) and [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ju*uwEN","text_ar":"جُذُوعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb.) ―         -b2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beam of a roof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n5330","headword_ar":"جَذَعٌ","root":"j*E","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A beast (Lth, Mgh)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaniY~","text_ar":"ثَنِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.], (Lth, S, Mgh, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by one year; when it may for the first time be ridden and used:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth:) fem. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Mgh, Msb, K:) pl. masc. [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^jo*aAEN","text_ar":"اجْذَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Yoo, O) and [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ju*oEaAnN","text_ar":"جُذْعَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Yoo, S, Mgh, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ji*oEaAnN","text_ar":"جِذْعَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ji*aAEN","text_ar":"جِذَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ju*aAEN","text_ar":"جُذَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Yoo, O;) and pl. fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ja*aEaAtN","text_ar":"جَذَعَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Msb:) it is a name applied to the beast in a particular time, not denoting a tooth growing or falling out: (S, K:) but it differs in its application to different kinds of beasts: (Az:) applied to a sheep or goat, it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a year old;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his second year:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or, applied to a sheep,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a year old;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and sometimes"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"less than a year,"},{"kind":"text","text":"by reason of plenty of food; (IAar;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eight months old,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, Mgh, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nine;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) or, when from young parents,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from six months old to seven;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and when from very old parents"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from eight months old to ten;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, Mgh;) and the sheep thus called is a satisfactory victim for sacrifice: (Mgh, TA:) and applied to a goat,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a year old;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, Mgh;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in its second year;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ;) but the goat thus called is not a satisfactory victim for sacrifice: (Mgh:) applied to a bull, it means in like manner"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his second year;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his third year;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the bull thus called is not a satisfactory victim for sacrifice: (TA:) applied to a horse, it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his third year;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his fourth year:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) [but see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAriHN","text_ar":"قَارِحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] and applied to a camel,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his fifth year;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, Mgh;) fem. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and this (a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"j*Ep","text_ar":"جذعة"},{"kind":"text","text":") is what must be given for the poor-rate when the camels are more than sixty. (Az, TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aSarN","text_ar":"شَصَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A youth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young man."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b3-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One who is light-witted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weak and stupid, like a youth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"opposed in this sense to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAzilN","text_ar":"بَازِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning “ old: ” (IAar, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one whose teeth have fallen out, here and there,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as though likened to a beast thus termed that has shed some of his first teeth,] because he has drawn near to his appointed term of life. (TA: [but it is not quite clear whether this explanation relate to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"j*E","text_ar":"جذع"},{"kind":"text","text":"or to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAzl","text_ar":"بازل"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b4-  (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A novice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"recent beginner."},{"kind":"text","text":"] You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY h`*aA AlA^amori ja*aEN","text_ar":"فِى هٰذَا الاَمْرِ جَذَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one, in this affair, is a novice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"recent beginner,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] when he has begun it recently. (S, Z.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~ahoru ja*aEN A^abadFA","text_ar":"الدَّهْرُ جَذَعٌ اَبَدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Time,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fortune, is ever new, like a youth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.) ―         -b6-  Hence, (TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^azolamu Alja*aEu","text_ar":"الاَزْلَمُ الجَذَعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Time,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fortune;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aholakahumu","text_ar":"اَهْلَكَهُمُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^azolamu Alja*aEu","text_ar":"الاَزْلَمُ الجَذَعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Time,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fortune, destroyed them;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA A=tiyka AlA^azolama Alja*aEa","text_ar":"لَا ا=تِيكَ الاَزْلَمَ الجَذَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will not come to thee ever."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See also art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zlm","text_ar":"زلم"},{"kind":"text","text":".] And accord. to some, (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The lion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) but this is a mistake. (IB, L.) ―         -b7-  And hence, (TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^um~u Alja*aEi","text_ar":"اُمُّ الجَذَعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Calamity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"misfortune."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEadotu AlA^amora ja*aEFA","text_ar":"اَعَدْتُ الاَمْرَ جَذَعًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I renewed the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair, as it was at the first:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as, for instance, a war which had been extinguished. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"far~a AlA^amora ja*aEFA","text_ar":"فَرَّ الاَمْرَ جَذَعًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[signifies, in like manner, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He recommenced the thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he commenced the thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fur~a AlA^amoru","text_ar":"فُرَّ الاَمْرُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ja*aEFA","text_ar":"جَذَعًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The thing was commenced:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the thing returned to its first state; it recommenced."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fr","text_ar":"فر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ju*oEaAnu AljibaAli","text_ar":"جُذْعَانُ الجِبَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Small mountains."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["Lth","Mgh","S","Msb","K","Yoo","O","L","Az","TA","IAar"]}]}}